    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Samsung R&D India. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Frontend Developer to strengthen our Noida-based team.\n\nAbout Samsung R&D India:\nSamsung R&D India is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Implement new features based on product requirements\n• Ensure code security and follow best practices for data protection\n• Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Tech / B.E. in Computer Science or related discipline\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in TypeScript\n• Proficiency in Node.js\n• Proficiency in Python\n• Proficiency in Agile/Scrum\n• Proficiency in Git\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in MongoDB\n• Proficiency in Kubernetes\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Flexible working hours\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Noida, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Samsung R&D India!",
